author: IGN
description: Check out Zero Point's story so far for Fortnite, the hit third-person battle royale game developed by Epic Games. Throughout history, the Zero Point has secretly connected civilizations, and for over a thousand years, the Imagined Order controlled the Zero Point, trapping people in an endless loop. Seven heroes came together to battle the Imagined Order and free the Zero Point. The battle ended with the Zero Point shattered and strewn across all realities, and the fate of the seven is unknown.
title: Fortnite’s Zero Point: The Story So Far

author: IGN
description:
Get a fresh look at Lekano World in this new trailer for the upcoming creature-collecting online action-adventure with MMO elements. Catch, Train, and Fight in real-time PvP arenas. Tame unique creatures in an open world and conquer your rivals. Lekano World will be available on PC, and the Playtest Arena is out now on Steam. You can learn more about the game if you're interested on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3552240/LEKANO_WORLD_ONLINE/ and Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/lekanoworldonline/lekano-world-online
